      <p><strong>Days 8–14 — Welcome by intent.</strong> Launch Sequenzy welcome paths: collection-page signup gets fit guide and size chart; giveaway signup gets brand story without immediate discount escalation; post-purchase customers route to education, not stranger offers. Priority plays from segment data: {segment.emailPriorities.join('; ')}.</p>
