      <h2>Common mistakes fashion stores make with Shopify email marketing apps</h2>
      <p><strong>Mistake 1 — Same welcome for drop hype and footer signups.</strong> Giveaway and influencer traffic needs brand story and size education, not immediate 15% off. Footer signups from collection browsers need fit guides for that collection. One welcome path trains the wrong expectation and inflates {segment.metrics[2]}.</p>
