      <p><strong>Mistake 4 — Three senders, zero collision calendar.</strong> Privy capture, Sequenzy lifecycle, and Postscript SMS each firing independently during drop week is the silent killer of {segment.metrics[3]}. One retention owner, one shared suppression doc.</p>
